{"tid":475983,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺以前讀書身邊總有啲好撚嘔心既同學","createTime":"2017-11-21T15:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T05:11:40.000Z","uid":16765,"like":461,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1e541d540a61e2859fd33497877af67cc6eb10","tid":475983,"uid":16765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"成撚日問佢有冇溫書<br />\n佢總會話無<br />\n但成績一出佢總會係好撚高分<br />\n哩啲人出黎做野都應該好撚虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b248e2d794ce8526d322acda35ba8014e3d257","tid":475983,"uid":32973,"like":1443,"dislike":19,"score":1424,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會係人地真係冇溫書都高分過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"9767c586ad4aa4639d9d97dbfc2f71a486912ac1","tid":475983,"uid":10325,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人地真係冇溫書都高分過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53844e1a0a1a2ece31c1f3030fe09f62749138c","tid":475983,"uid":87506,"like":390,"dislike":6,"score":384,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"考天才波勁過你又唔撚得既<br />\n屌你老母 溫完都咁撚廢死左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n屈撚完未阿仆街 單單打打咁"},{"pid":"a922f1c533fb328378f4e042a6c9fd7ee62a1454","tid":475983,"uid":10325,"like":3,"dislike":43,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人地真係冇溫書都高分過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\nsorry唔小心比左負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beee11b733e31ef8df89451aeffb19a3aa1f354c","tid":475983,"uid":33060,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"我以為做過D咩行為<br />\n<br />\n屌,依D樣係天分黎<br />\n人地平時聽書聽得入腦已經記得,唔洗溫書,只係做下功課加深印象唔得既咩<br />\n<br />\n你讀極唔入腦,有撚計呀"},{"pid":"471155419f29bad286fa2b923dbad723ede2a852","tid":475983,"uid":149534,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以為做過D咩行為<br />\n<br />\n屌,依D樣係天分黎<br />\n人地平時聽書聽得入腦已經記得,唔洗溫書,只係做下功課加深印象唔得既咩<br />\n<br />\n你讀極唔入腦,有撚計呀</blockquote><br />\nAgree， 有樣野叫SQ3R，用的好真係唔洗點溫書。<br />\n<br />\n另外，to樓主， 你如果真心溫極都未如理想， 點解唔試下請教其他同學？ 好有可能係你溫書個方式唔適合自己。<br />\n<br />\n到佢唔肯教你/ 老點你時你再開post鬧人都未遲。"},{"pid":"725efcd4db9d88fa8c53778820566e059a54be97","tid":475983,"uid":143269,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n答你溫咗 考得差俾你笑<br />\n答你無溫 考得好俾你話扮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512b90b7fe31a91cc794611066c667193a7f6fee","tid":475983,"uid":46231,"like":19,"dislike":11,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"但係講真 真係試過有年完全無溫書 上堂係到玩 但係考撚左第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5026a46dd3986bf1ec77549767c7a44bf8ec16d","tid":475983,"uid":39065,"like":131,"dislike":4,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"我就係你口中呢類人<br />\n<br />\n不如問下自己,我平時上堂認真聽書寫notes個陣<br />\n你地係到做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n我眼見屌柒我話唔溫但係又高分d人,平時上堂一係鳩hea一係訓教<br />\n臨考個陣就臨前一兩日先溫,咁都比你高分過我就真係無天理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你係又勤力但係又唔高分<br />\n不妨請教下身邊人,好過係到嘈嘈閉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b00cc2f0566c467c846d9642c873eb9b8c5e44d","tid":475983,"uid":54597,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到成日話無溫但有溫 不過好撚低GPA<br />\n成日大大聲話說乜都無睇無做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3367201f3455754ce1e19cd3d96884d5d4c4d93","tid":475983,"uid