c=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c881e202d35247ed5e28508982031a2cb0e6ecb","tid":475983,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"對唔住樓主，天生記性好都無辦法，唔通識答都因為同你講左句無溫書就特登考低分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eabf00679166275762ae1f7386b8380efe77c2e","tid":475983,"uid":61910,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"以為你講上堂玩口水鼻涕頭皮老泥個D"},{"pid":"1c2843fdec2c1cf982cb825afacbc96259457836","tid":475983,"uid":55511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"睇到傻鳩樓主比大家圍住屌 me真係老懷安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a05f964df192a9917f70f447b310a89349fac3","tid":475983,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"Sor<br />\n唔太溫書<br />\n9讀1take入u"},{"pid":"453f47a53b4bfb284aeb9f10f8a8a50b0ec1d485","tid":475983,"uid":136632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"我無溫呀 諗住唔溫算 放棄學業喇唉<br />\n點知轉頭見佢狂溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6c511048bc717e5bf039b896a1e352a76533f6","tid":475983,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"無溫書同高分無衝突<br />\n<br />\n話唔撚識又次次都高分就話啫"},{"pid":"f71f74013f6769c5ecb0c6f284504cdf371a5d28","tid":475983,"uid":30694,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"講真冇溫都高過你係咪要檢討下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16af5db5777bdbcf50f57b4eabd835dba2b0fa89","tid":475983,"uid":52683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬去左溫書喇 廢事下次又唔合格會俾媽咪鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"h