kgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你係又勤力但係又唔高分<br />\n不妨請教下身邊人,好過係到嘈嘈閉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔小心㩒錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf0c44faf79261a83f1f531c2fa49334a514e59","tid":475983,"uid":30804,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌,成班on9係度搵位讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地講緊呢個行為虛偽呀<br />\n理得你天才定讀書啫<br />\n唔駛讀書都考到高分關我lun事<br />\n係屌9啲假人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正常 <br />\n連登仔個個都係天才 iq200 <br />\n記性又好 過目不忘 <br />\n唔溫書拎高分 其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天才同虛偽差好撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面串樓主嗰班人正笨柒<br />\n樓主擺明講班考試前叫哂救命話溫唔撚切 考完話炒撚硬 派卷就頭十嗰啲人（但多數都唔係頭一二 資質有限 真正天才先拎頭一二）<br />\n真心勁嗰啲天才就算真係過目不忘都唔會開口埋口話自己唔使溫<br />\n我唔信樓上回覆嗰班未遇過依種人<br />\n(可能佢地自己就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ebd0e486394662669f04ecc6dec883997acee373","tid":475983,"uid":158242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"係，佢問你野唔識就屌你，你問返佢野佢就會話我唔會答你"},{"pid":"220a815c10bf4546d1b1190572711536a04f747e","tid":475983,"uid":143269,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌,成班on9係度搵位讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地講緊呢個行為虛偽呀<br />\n理得你天才定讀書啫<br />\n唔駛讀書都考到高分關我lun事<br />\n係屌9啲假人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" c